DISCIPLINARY CASES

1996-0297. In re Resignation of Renshaw.

By order dated March 6,1996, the court accepted the affidavit of resignation of Robert E. Renshaw in which he acknowledged that the resignation was final, unconditional and irrevocable.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing by Robert E. Renshaw of an application for reinstatement. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by this court that the application be, and hereby is, denied.
